vin Davies|access-date=15 April 2016}}</ref>\n|Premier League\n|31||6||4||2||2||0||colspan=2|\u2014||37||8\n|-\n|[[2012\u201313 Bolton Wanderers F.C. season|2012\u201313]]<ref name=\"Games played by Kevin Davies in 2012/2013\">{{Soccerbase season|1943|2012|name=Kevin Davies|access-date=15 April 2016}}</ref>\n|[[EFL Championship|Championship]]\n|35||6||2||0||1||0||colspan=2|\u2014||38||6\n|-\n!colspan=2|Total\n!351!!74!!25!!8!!18!!2!!13!!1!!407!!85\n|-\n|rowspan=3|[[Preston North End F.C.|Preston North End]]\n|[[2013\u201314 Preston North End F.C. season|2013\u201314]]<ref name=\"Games played by Kevin Davies in 2013/2014\">{{Soccerbase season|1943|2013|name=Kevin Davies|access-date=15 April 2016}}</ref>\n|[[EFL League One|League One]]\n|38||3||4||2||2||0||2{{efn|Appearances in [[EFL League One play-offs|League One play-offs]]}}||0||46||5\n|-\n|[[2014\u201315 Preston North End F.C. season|2014\u201315]]<ref name=\"SW\">{{cite web |title=K. Davies |url=https://int.soccerway.com/players/kevin-cyril-davies/2634/ |work=Soccerway |publisher=Perform Group |accessdate=15 April 2016}}</ref>\n|League One\n|32||1||5||0||2||0||5{{efn|Four appearances in Football League Trophy, one in League One play-offs}}||0||44||1\n|-\n!colspan=2|Total\n!70!!4!!9!!2!!4!!0!!7!!0!!90!!6\n|-\n!colspan=3|Career total\n!689!!123!!55!!19!!43!!7!!31!!2!!818!!151\n|}\n\n{{notelist}}\n\n===International===\n{| class=wikitable style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|+ Appearances and goals by national team and year\n|-\n!National team!!Year!!Apps!!Goals\n|-\n|[[England national football team|England]]<ref>{{NFT player |id=25387 |name=Davies, Kevin |accessdate=15 April 2016}}</ref>\n|2010||1||0\n|-\n!colspan=2|Total!!1!!0\n|}\n\n==Managerial statistics==\n{{updated|match played 28 April 2018}}\n\n{| class=wikitable style=\"text-align: center\"\n|+ Managerial record by team and tenure\n|-\n!rowspan=2|Team\n!rowspan=2|From\n!rowspan=2|To\n!colspan=5|Record\n!rowspan=2|{{abbr|Ref|Reference}}\n|-\n!{{abbr|P|Matches 